c: 2
v: 232
t: "Ne olwamulalekha Abakhasi ne nibamala induukho yabu mulabekalila okhutekha khubatsa babu nikali mbu banyolane khubulayi , kano yekanyilisibwa khuko ulia owasuubila Nyasaye nende inyanga yeyindukho, kano ni amalayi khwinywe ne amalafu muno Ne Nyasaye amanyile halali enywe shimumanyile tawe"